nce in Application Performance Managing /Real User Monitoring, infrastructure monitoring and log analysis tool such as Dynatrace, Nagios, Sensu and Splunk. 5+ yrs. of experience with DevOps, Continuous Delivery Expertise in working in partnership with colleagues throughout the firm, and in leading collaborative teams to achieve common goals Experience in an Agile delivery environment ", 
